&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;10 month fixed term contract maternity leave cover. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be required to provide a comprehensive, highly skilled clinical support to Cornwall Partnership Foundation Trust Podiatry Team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Multi-disciplinary working will be an important aspect of this role to ensure best outcomes for the patient. Sharing of best practice with podiatrists and other relevant clinicians will be key to this role, as will involve patients, carers and support agencies in delivery of care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role will provide an opportunity for the successful candidate to experience a full range of podiatry care provision.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Clinical caseloads will be managed based on experience and clinical supervision will be provided in the agreed CPFT Podiatry structure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name Liza Downing&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title Podiatry Team Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address liza.downing@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number07824 838158&lt;/p&gt;
